                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-10">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-12 col-md-5">
                                    <h4 class="card-title heading-4">
                                        <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none black">
                                            Diffuse 24x24: 59575
